24:16.734 --> 24:21.861
trying to make a role for myself here. I am trying to 
make a role for talented women here that are

24:22.642 --> 24:37.002
generally known as the tremendous teachers at 
Texas A&M, the wonderful counselors for the

24:22.642 --> 24:37.002
students, the great service providers. but not 
the decision makers. And if we don't change that,

